<Base title="Skin Deep — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Skin Deep</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">CUAT Sadka (Cracow Art Week KRAKERS 2023) | 2023</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>I know that you have a fragile heart. I promise to touch it carefully.</p>
      <p>The exhibition explores intimate spaces through the lens of body art. Tattoos function as personal archives—a record of stories, memories, fleeting moments etched permanently onto skin's surface. Tiny blemishes, scars, souvenirs on skin's canvas. Their wobbly lines, tribal motifs, quotes from songs, personal symbols extend metaphorically throughout domestic space, transforming the bedroom into a gallery where body markings, bedding patterns, and architectural elements merge into a cohesive statement about impermanence, desire, and memory preservation.</p>
      <p>Today is the day. We are about to go to this place where time flies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Curator:</strong> Michalina Sablik</p>
      <p><strong>Performance Curator:</strong> Kornel Le&#347;niak</p>
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Jakub Gli&#324;ski, Kornel Le&#347;niak, Marcjanna, Ola Nenko, Monika Przygodzka, Mateusz Sarzy&#324;ski, Stach Szumski</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
